the government calls it zero tolerance 
but industry and civil liberties groups have begun to question 
whether overkill isnt an equally accurate description of the 
policy under which luxury yachts and other private property is 
being seized in the battle against drugs 
in the latest episode the us coast guard confiscated on 
saturay the yacht monkey business the charter vessel that once 
ferried presidential contender gary hart and model donna rice to 
the bahamas after officers said they found 1 gram or one 
twentyeighth of an ounce of marijuana aboard 
