yacht ark royal on grounds that onetenth of an ounce of 
marijuana was aboard no one was arrested in either case 
even rental cars and leased boats and trucks are being seized by 
us customs service agents and the coast guard triggering 
complaints from owners who argue that they shouldnt be penalized 
for the acts of their customers 
richard schwartz president of the boat owners association of 
