budget committee next year said he was concerned congress was 
ceding back to the executive branch the economic decisionmaking 
prowess it has fought to gain 
i think congress has to be very concerned when it begins to 
lose what has been an objective eye in dealing with budget 
issues he said without an officiallyappointed leader to carry 
the flag the agency is an easier target for those who dont like 
cbos opinions he said 
the agency is already embroiled in a dispute between house 
